OL,3,CMilburn warns of a lost generation
OL,4,Ctrapped by welfare and job shortages
OL,6,FThe Milburn Review argues that young
OL,7,Fpeople in Britain face a crisis
OL,8,Fprevious generations have not -
OL,9,Fsqueezed between a lack of
OL,10,Fopportunities and institutions that
OL,11,Fare failing them.
OL,13,FSchools are not preparing enough young
OL,14,Fpeople for life in the workplace.
OL,16,FThe welfare system traps young people
OL,17,Fon benefits.
OL,19,FThe NHS deems too many unfit for work.
OL,20,FAnd entry-level jobs are drying up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
