OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780038278
OL,3,CMilburn warns of a lost generation
OL,4,Ctrapped by welfare and job shortages
OL,6,F"It's a perfect storm," Alan Milburn
OL,7,Ftold me, "and it's getting worse."
OL,9,FAt the launch of his interim report,
OL,10,Fwhich was strong on diagnosis but
OL,11,Flight on cures he said: "It sometimes
OL,12,Ffeels there aren't many causes left in
OL,13,Fmodern British politics. But this is
OL,14,Fone.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@WO]oD@JOUoD@bO]sD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780038278
OL,3,CMilburn warns of a lost generation
OL,4,Ctrapped by welfare and job shortages
OL,6,F"The scale and impact of this problem
OL,7,Fcan no longer be ignored. We cannot
OL,8,Fthrow a whole generation of young
OL,9,Fpeople on the scrapheap before their
OL,10,Fadult lives have properly begun."
OL,12,FFor the first time, the number of
OL,13,Fyoung people in the UK not in
OL,14,Feducation, employment or training has
OL,15,Frisen above one million.
OL,17,FThat is 13.5% of all 16- to 24-year-
OL,18,Folds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780038278
OL,3,CMilburn warns of a lost generation
OL,4,Ctrapped by welfare and job shortages
OL,6,FThat rate means Britain is almost
OL,7,Fbottom of the table compared with
OL,8,Fother European countries - only
OL,9,FRomania performs worse.
OL,11,FFrance, Germany, Ireland and the
OL,12,FNetherlands all do a much better job
OL,13,Fof supporting young people into work.
OL,15,FThe Milburn Review says one reason is
OL,16,Fthat for every #25 the government
OL,17,Fspends on benefits for young people,
OL,18,Fonly #1 is spent on employment support.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
