CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780038278
OL,3,CMilburn warns of a lost generation
OL,4,Ctrapped by welfare and job shortages
OL,6,FMilburn highlights another issue:
OL,7,Fyoung people today are more likely to
OL,8,Fsuffer from anxiety and depression,
OL,9,Fand he insists social media is "a big
OL,10,Fpart" of the problem.
OL,12,F"We've had a small team of people
OL,13,Fgoing out across the country talking
OL,14,Fto literally hundreds of young people
OL,15,Fwho are not in education, employment
OL,16,For training," he told ITV News.
OL,26,@qD@`OUrD@EO]tD@AOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780038278
OL,3,CMilburn warns of a lost generation
OL,4,Ctrapped by welfare and job shortages
OL,6,F"They asked them a question. They
OL,7,Fsaid: 'What time did you go to sleep
OL,8,Flast night?' Two o'clock. Three
OL,9,Fo'clock. Four o'clock. Five o'clock.
OL,10,FSometimes never. What are these young
OL,11,Fpeople doing, living in their
OL,12,Fbedrooms? Doom-scrolling on their
OL,13,Fphones."
OL,15,FDoes he support a ban on social media
OL,16,Ffor the under-16s? He won't say but
OL,17,Foffers this hint: "Personally, I think
OL,18,Fthe evidence is pretty overwhelming."
OL,20,FGovernment policy is also under
OL,21,Fscrutiny.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@HO]yD@SOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
