CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780038278
OL,3,CMilburn warns of a lost generation
OL,4,Ctrapped by welfare and job shortages
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister called the report
OL,7,F"sobering" and pledged to work with
OL,8,FAlan Milburn on solutions.
OL,10,FAlthough Keir Starmer may no longer be
OL,11,FPrime Minister by the time the final
OL,12,Frecommendations are published in
OL,13,FSeptember.
OL,15,FThe proposals are likely to be radical.
OL,17,F"It is not about yet more iterative
OL,18,Freform," warned Milburn. "It is about
OL,19,Fa fundamental system reset."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@JO]yD@AOUzD@HO]zD@ZOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
